member.summary:
This allows for setting up a Flex price type "category" for a MOS.  This keeps flex price types from showing up in single ticket areas
Default:    (none)
Format:     FLEX_PRICE_TYPE_CATEGORY_MOS_{0}

This allows for setting up a Flex price type ID's for a MOS.  This keeps flex price types from showing up in single ticket areas
Default:    (none)
Format:     FLEX_PRICE_TYPE_MOS_{0}

This setting allows for setting up an explicit list of price type ID's for a MOS
Default:    (none)
Format:     DEFAULT_PRICE_TYPE_{0}

This setting allows for setting up an explicit list of price types allowed for a MOS and promo
Default:    (none)
Format:     ALLOW_ONLY_PRICE_TYPE_MOS_{0}_PROMO_{1}

This setting allows for setting up an explicit list of price type ID's allowed for a MOS
Default:    (none)
Format:     ALLOW_ONLY_PRICE_TYPE_MOS_{0}

This setting allows for setting up an explicit list of price type "categories" for a MOS
Default:    (none)
Format:     ALLOW_ONLY_PRICE_TYPE_CATEGORY_MOS_{0}

This setting allows for setting up an explicit list of price type "categories" for a MOS and a particular promo (useful for the default MOS / promo)
Default:    (none)
Format:     ALLOW_ONLY_PRICE_TYPE_CATEGORY_MOS_{0}_PROMO_{1}

This setting allows for setting up an explicit list of price type "categories" for a MOS to be excluded from the website
Default:    (none)
Format:     DISALLOW_PRICE_TYPE_CATEGORY_MOS_{0}

This setting allows for setting up an explicit list of price type "categories" for a MOS to be excluded from the website
Default:    (none)
Format:     DISALLOW_PRICE_TYPE_CATEGORY_MOS_{0}_PROMO_{1}

This setting allows for setting up an explicit list of price type ID's disalloed for a MOS and promo
Default:    (none)
Format:     DISALLOW_PRICE_TYPE_CATEGORY_MOS_{0}_PROMO_{1}

This setting allows for setting up an explicit list of price type ID's disalloed for a MOS
Default:    (none)
Format:     DISALLOW_PRICE_TYPE_MOS_{0}

This setting allows for setting up an explicit list of price type "categories" for a MOS to be excluded from the website
Default:    (none)
Format:     DISALLOW_PRICE_TYPE_CATEGORY_IF_NOT_PROMO_MOS{0}

This setting allows for setting up an explicit list of price type for a MOS to if it isn't coming through as a promo price type
Default:    (none)
Format:     DISALLOW_PRICE_TYPE_IF_NOT_PROMO_MOS_{0}

This setting allows for setting up an explicit list of price type for a MOS to if it isn't coming through as a promo price type
Default:    (none)
Format:     DISALLOW_PRICE_TYPE_IF_NOT_PROMO_BY_DESC_MOS_{0}
